As of the [[census]]<ref name=census>{{cite web | title = U.S. Census website | url = https://www.census.gov | publisher = [[United States Census Bureau]] | access-date = May 18, 2011}}</ref> of 2010, there were 56 people living in the CDP. There were 31 housing units. The [[Race and ethnicity in the United States census|ethnic makeup]] of the town was 96.4% White and 3.6% American Native and Alaska Native. Hispanic or Latino of any race were 19.6% of the population.

